      <title>星巴克 ChatGPT 测试版上线：AI点单正在改写咖啡数字化竞争规则</title>
      <link>https://www.coffeeprism.com/posts/xing-ba-ke-chatgpt-ce-shi-ban-shang-xian-aidian-da/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 19:03:12 +0800</pubDate>
